<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-6871] Log compenent removes line separators from logged message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6871</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Steps&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Send exchange with input body equal to &lt;tt&gt;&quot;1&quot; + LS + &quot;2&quot; + LS + &quot;3&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;, where &lt;tt&gt;LS&lt;/tt&gt; is a system dependent line separator.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Log exchange input body with Camel log component:
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;to uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;log:logger_name?level=INFO&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Expected&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Exchange input body is logged with &lt;tt&gt;LS&lt;/tt&gt; charcters preserved:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;1
2
3&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Observed&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Exchange is logged without &lt;tt&gt;LS&lt;/tt&gt; characters:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;123&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Workaround&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Use log EIP instead:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;log loggingLevel=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;INFO&quot;&lt;/span&gt; logName=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;logger_name&quot;&lt;/span&gt; message=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${body}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
