                            <comment id="13800642" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 21 Oct 2013 13:32:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adding option &lt;tt&gt;skipBodyLineSeparator&lt;/tt&gt; so people can configure if they want to skip the LS or not. This preserves current behavior as default.&lt;/p&gt;

